column5: hasnt been in previous years... just be back by the set time

Christoper,just walk out til you find 50 fow and work your way out and around. You wont have to walk that far. Ones with sleds, will be traveling 8-10 miles.

Half a mile do east from the launch,you will find it. Bring a map,I,ll point ya in the right direction.  One more sleep.

Leaving Hammertown around 4.30 should be there around 6.30 see everybody there

Just a reminder to folks to bring CASH for the silent auction.  I know in the past we would have purchased many more of the fine items available but didn't have cash on hand, just makes it easier.  Tony
